reviewText:
The copyright on the box says 1997, but based on the look of it - the hairstyles, the clothes, the phones, the over-inflated breast enhancements - I'd say it's more like 1990 to 1992. That and the Casio-tone 'score' are reason enough to watch this one, for ironic enjoyment.

It's basically a porno with no actual porn per se, i.e. no penetration shots, etc. However, the female nudity is full, as are the actresses boobs (of silicone, not milk). The scans of the box art here should give you a pretty good idea of what to expect.

This would make a great party tape when people start having '90s retro-themed get-togethers. (Are they already..?)

This movie was soo HOT!!!!1!
I especially liked the scene with the male temp and a donkey.  When they brought in the donuts, I thought I was going to LOSE IT!!~!!  Ha ha ha, if you know what I mean.
